search and import youtube videos simple php mysql application example using the CakePHP php framework...

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Installation:

git clone https://github.com/andraskende/youtube-scraper-cakephp-app.git /var/www/domain.com/

cd /var/www/domain.com/

git submodule init

git submodule update

copy Config/database.php.default to Config/database.php and edit database settings

import .sql files from Config/Schema

chmod -R 777 tmp/

domain.com/admin/videos/

admin login:  admin/admin

